  <brief_title>Efficacy and Safety Study of Eprotirome in HeFH Patients Who Are on Optimal Standard of Care</brief_title>
  <acronym>AKKA</acronym>
  <official_title>A Placebo-controlled, Double-blind, Randomised, Parallel-group, Long Term Phase III Trial Assessing the Safety and Efficacy of Eprotirome in Patients With Heterozygous Familial Hypercholesterolaemia Who Are on Optimal Standard of Care</official_title>
